</h3><p class="sc-kHOZwM oQMan pf-21_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Personal protective equipment in first aid includes items designed to protect against injuries or infections during the provision of care. Common PPE includes gloves, masks, eye protection, and more. These items are crucial in creating a barrier against potential contaminants and injuries.

</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-iqseJM ducrfW pf-23_ pf-r pf-c-lm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fHeRUh cCunWv pf-24_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bTfYFJ fFWOZc pf-25_ pf-heading-1-h3">Key facts and statistics</h3><p class="sc-kHOZwM oQMan pf-27_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Research indicates that proper use of PPE can reduce the risk of infection in emergency situations by up to 95%.<br></p><p class="sc-kHOZwM oQMan pf-29_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">The application of PPE is considered a best practice in the prevention of disease transmission during first aid responses.
</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-iqseJM ducrfW pf-31_ pf-r pf-c-lm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fHeRUh cCunWv pf-32_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bTfYFJ fFWOZc pf-33_ pf-heading-1-h3">Definitions and relevance</h3><p class="sc-kHOZwM oQMan pf-35_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3"><strong>Personal Protective Equipment (PPE)</strong> - Items that protect users against health or safety risks. In first aid, this typically includes gloves, masks, protective eyewear, and aprons.</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-iqseJM ducrfW pf-37_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fHeRUh cCunWv pf-38_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bTfYFJ fFWOZc pf-39_ pf-heading-1-h3">Legislation and regulations
</h3><p class="sc-kHOZwM oQMan pf-41_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Understanding and complying with PPE-related legislation is essential for safety:

