</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah hUMvDY pf-46_ pf-text-1"><strong>Personal Protective Equipment at Work Regulations 1992 (as amended)</strong> - Specific to PPE, these regulations mandate that employers provide appropriate protective equipment where risks cannot be adequately controlled by other means.





