</p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-kYHfwS lkFAWj pf-54_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah hUMvDY pf-55_ pf-text-1"><strong>Proper selection and use</strong> - Choose PPE that is suitable for the type of first aid being provided and ensure it fits correctly.



</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah hUMvDY pf-57_ pf-text-1"><strong>Training</strong> - Regular training on the correct use, limitations, and care of PPE is essential for all potential first aid responders.





